                                  BACKGROUNDPEN
                                      This   pen  is   used   to   fill  the
                                      background of an unselected gadget.

                                  HIGHLIGHTTEXTPEN
                                      This pen is used to draw the text of a
                                      gadget   with   the  HighLight  switch
